{"tid":2232093,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Golden Scene Cinema裝修進行中","createTime":"2020-10-06T06:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T08:05:42.000Z","uid":51446,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8c676bcebc5049d67f9c677fac8ab4ba25f5453e","tid":2232093,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"西環北街海怡花園三座外所攝，有關戲院的位置已圍上圍板，並且寫上「Golden Scene Cinema」的名字，其標誌的風格，跟高先電影發行相若。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0B5B7336-9242-4BA9-BDAE-1B5E5AF95C73.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F0B5B7336-9242-4BA9-BDAE-1B5E5AF95C73.jpeg&h=1992d0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DE8CB974-7A23-4D3A-AC7E-47E960246847.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FDE8CB974-7A23-4D3A-AC7E-47E960246847.jpeg&h=cf7711fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/78109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F78109&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=68652d23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/78109</a>"},{"pid":"1161a8f8f1d1a2916a8afac254498acf5c741681","tid":2232093,"uid":51446,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200420/7DIW4CLN6DVFGFQGAWPXVOEBYA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200420%2F7DIW4CLN6DVFGFQGAWPXVOEBYA%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=cb58b228\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200420%2F7DIW4CLN6DVFGFQGAWPXVOEBYA%2F&h=062ead1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200420/7DIW4CLN6DVFGFQGAWPXVOEBYA/</a><br />\nGolden Scene老闆曾麗芬（Winnie）今日回覆《蘋果》，證實於年底會在堅尼地城開一間戲院，她表示：「我一直想有自己戲院，因以前喺嘉禾時期，我都有管理戲院，所以成立自己院線咁多年，一直想有自己戲院。我上年簽約租地方時都未有疫情發生，我都有信心今年底開張時疫情會過去，唔會影響生意，我希望可以開4、5間戲院，但唔會太急進，等第一間做得住，先會陸續開落去。」"},{"pid":"24e88f160b977ef6d98f78de3c5827703c3be226","tid":2232093,"uid":42848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FYcvxh20XFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFYcvxh20XFs&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=3ce8d0c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FYcvxh20XFs</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6096276f536dc4fb33e8fb436db66ae293783575","tid":2232093,"uid":36455,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"整合定高先出品精選list<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c899021a73434ebb55931f5dd6353d959685424d","tid":2232093,"uid":48479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:20:14.000Z","msg":"Golden Scenema<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32811376b47be1c8ab83f07b4c7b916478115c64","tid":2232093,"uid":300687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T19:40:54.000Z","msg":"四五個院都幾進取 以為好似外國repertory cinema咁一大一細<br />\n希望搞得成功啦"},{"pid":"e03c899dfd5f4939017bfbbc107b30ade1c06da5","tid":2232093,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32811376b47be1c8ab83f07b4c7b916478115c64","tid":2232093,"uid":300687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score