Z","msg":"共產黨打到嚟喇，仲開戲院嫌錢多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d05907276e85b51463bc7793096ff57d83e9ee0","tid":2232093,"uid":44815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:25:27.000Z","msg":"快d開到區區都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e3b145928a0bb9f47e95fc23d808a64a599dce","tid":2232093,"uid":147029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"小型戲院？"},{"pid":"f0de6013701a54946fc2091d2c49c41ca234a144","tid":2232093,"uid":51446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"王宗堯有份主演(其中一個單元故事)的香港本土獨立電影《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》由去年開始參加不同影展, 而家終於搵到香港發行商!<br />\n《十年》《幻愛》的發行商Golden Scene已經取得《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》香港發行權!   Golden Scene現在已安排《夜香．鴛鴦．深水埗》在本星期六於藝術中心古天樂電影院放映優先場, 但正式上映日期未定."},{"pid":"17db21a41c33acfd5d32befdf44821fd47989e29","tid":2232093,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T13:19:48.000Z","msg":"嘩，原來喺Golden Scence 戲院，以後可以瘋狂睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb924f9a1a04a208a3c5c763da9f41e604b73df","tid":2232093,"uid":176104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:05:42.000Z","msg":"聽日開喇喂 全日狂舞派無限loop"}]}